        {
            "id": "using-app",
            "type": "screen",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "className": "alert",
                    "text": "SECTION: USING THE APP"
                },
                "",
                "Core header controls:",
                "- SCRIPT: switch bundled/custom/module scripts",
                "- MODULES: manage your own and subscribed modules",
                "- CREATOR: edit the active script or start a script",
                "- RELOAD: restart the active script runtime from the beginning",
                "- RESET: clear broader local app state (more aggressive)",
                "- THEME + SOUND controls",
                "",
                "Preview mode details:",
                "- Header shows [PREVIEW MODE] + [RETURN TO CREATOR]",
                "- Flow runs in the real terminal renderer",
                "- Use it before publishing modules",
                "",
                "Tip: SHIFT+SPACE skips active typing animation.",
                "",
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "text": "> NEXT: MODULES + LIBRARY WORKFLOW",
                    "target": "modules-workflow"
                },
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "text": "> TABLE OF CONTENTS",
                    "target": "hub"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "modules-workflow",
            "type": "screen",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "className": "alert",
                    "text": "SECTION: MODULES + LIBRARY WORKFLOW"
                },
                "",
                "Visibility modes:",
                "- private: visible only to your account",
                "- unlisted: available through direct link and hidden from library listings",
                "- public: visible in the library and shareable",
                "",
                "Modules panel capabilities:",
                "- My Modules: load, view in library, copy link (shareable only)",
                "- Subscribed Modules: load, view in library, manage script dropdown visibility",
                "- Show in SCRIPT checkboxes decide what appears in the SCRIPT dropdown",
                "",
                "Share links:",
                "- Public and unlisted modules support link-based loading",
                "- Unlisted is ideal for direct sharing without catalog exposure",
                "",
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "text": "> NEXT: SCRIPT CREATOR WORKFLOW",
                    "target": "creator-workflow"
                },
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "text": "> PREVIOUS: USING THE APP",
                    "target": "using-app"
                },
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "text": "> TABLE OF CONTENTS",
                    "target": "hub"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "creator-workflow",
            "type": "screen",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "className": "alert",
                    "text": "SECTION: SCRIPT CREATOR WORKFLOW"
                },
                "",
                "1) Open CREATOR from header.",
                "2) Use NEW SCRIPT to start clean, or edit the active script.",
                "3) Build screens from the left list; dialogs are in a dedicated list mode.",
                "4) Add elements from the Add Element menu.",
                "5) Use [CONFIG: ON/OFF] to show or hide script config fields.",
                "6) Use [SCHEMA] to inspect connection flow across screens/dialogs.",
                "7) PREVIEW in runtime, then APPLY TO APP.",
                "8) Save/update as a module from the Modules panel.",
                "",
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "className": "notice",
                    "text": "Use Creator for quick iteration, flow debugging, and module publishing."
                },
                "",
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "text": "> NEXT: SCRIPT STRUCTURE",
                    "target": "script-structure"
                },
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "text": "> PREVIOUS: MODULES + LIBRARY",
                    "target": "modules-workflow"
                },
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "text": "> TABLE OF CONTENTS",
                    "target": "hub"
                }
            ]
        },
